{"tid":1832291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我屌你老母呀支那國 習種開完綠燈 周圍搶住報人數","createTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T22:55:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":465,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebcc03e5297c575b3f22755b7cb1d013c727d66","tid":1832291,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母支那政府唔好咁撚痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2日前仲係話受控 拉鳩左幾十人網上造謠<br />\n今日你同我講要嚴查瞞報官員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央政法委：肺炎疫情刻意遲報瞞報是千古罪人<br />\n中央政法委微信公眾號「長安劍」周二（21日）開腔談及防控工作，強調只有準確、及時公布相關信息，才能有效展開防控，把面子看得比民眾利益重的政客將是國家的千古罪人；為了一己之利刻意瞞報遲報，將釘在歷史的恥辱柱上。<br />\n「長安劍」的文章指，本次肺炎疫情讓許多人聯想到2003年的SARS疫情，但中國政府沒有重走當年SARS信息公布披露的那條老路。從上月首次公布疫情至今，21天時間內，僅武漢市衞健委發布的各類情況通報就有14次，信息公開力度不可謂不大。各個部門的行動也相繼展開，各項防控措施正在全面落實，防控疫情的相關知識正通過報紙、電視、互聯網向全社會普及。"},{"pid":"32b7161f687be8a641f762a2f37a0be697c26190","tid":1832291,"uid":52127,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"蓋清咁緊火做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa15967604f6be4f419c19743c67b76876d0383f","tid":1832291,"uid":308020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959910005e10dbc4addc7f179e1ad58c89eb8