公布相關信息，才能有效展開防控，把面子看得比民眾利益重的政客將是國家的千古罪人；為了一己之利刻意瞞報遲報，將釘在歷史的恥辱柱上。<br />\n「長安劍」的文章指，本次肺炎疫情讓許多人聯想到2003年的SARS疫情，但中國政府沒有重走當年SARS信息公布披露的那條老路。從上月首次公布疫情至今，21天時間內，僅武漢市衞健委發布的各類情況通報就有14次，信息公開力度不可謂不大。各個部門的行動也相繼展開，各項防控措施正在全面落實，防控疫情的相關知識正通過報紙、電視、互聯網向全社會普及。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"香港股市俾佢提前搞冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1959fabf3c273fe42e68cd82a97a545b6fed80","tid":1832291,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"大鳴大放WARS版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c649f880d0f4bc7f73454f40e915393a9386c6e4","tid":1832291,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"爭住鬥多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41142e9e43b32c4658039b04dc908fecb20b0aa7","tid":1832291,"uid":301952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"大鳴大放 引蛇出洞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a413bf85e56cd6a4b9f41fd99995f2eaac5b5e","tid":1832291,"uid":332713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"把面子看得比民眾利益重的政客將是國家的千古罪人；為了一己之利刻意瞞報遲報，將釘在歷史的恥辱柱上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f2a00188277ef86ec8b0ad3a1b6120e76dbf42","tid":1832291,"uid":198952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32b7161f687be8a641f762a2f37a0be697c26190","tid":1832291,"uid":52127,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"蓋清咁緊火做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:48:27.000Z","msg":"無得call g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ea